            <p>If you haven't seen it yet, check out the latest hi-tech accessory for everyday athletes—Comfe Arms. It's the first ever totally fabric armband with built-in bling. Comfe Arms uses a unique silver-impregnated fabric to kill bacteria that causes stink. Using the best moisture-wicking technology, the fabric stretches to a slim fit over your forearm and helps expel moisture instead of trapping it in thick fabrics or plastics. Comfe Arms provides the most comfortable running experience with a mobile device. And it's 100% made in the USA. Available for order on <a href="" target="_blank">Amazon.com.</a></p>
        </span>
