            <p>Today Comfe Designs launchd Comfe Hands, a first-of-its-kind product for tablets. Comfe Hands is an ergonomic accessory for iPad2 + iPad3 that makes reading / gaming / working with the tablets super comfy. Eliminate the painful "pinch grip" and feel in control of your game. Comfe Hands is 100% made in the USA from recyclable plastics. Available for order on <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Comfe-Designs-CH-004-Hands/dp/B0060MRBAY" target="_blank">Amazon.com.</a></p>
